                    <h2 class="mb-4">Our Journey</h2>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Sree Muthukumaraswamy College</strong> was established with a vision to impart quality higher education and promote academic excellence rooted in cultural values and social responsibility. Since its inception, the institution has been dedicated to nurturing young minds through holistic education, discipline, and moral strength.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Over the years, the college has evolved into a center of academic excellence, offering a wide range of undergraduate and postgraduate programs in arts, science, and commerce. Our focus has always been on creating a learner-centric environment that encourages curiosity, innovation, and critical thinking among students.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="mt-5 mb-4">Institutional Profile</h2>

                    <p>
                        Located in a serene and accessible part of the city, <strong>Sree Muthukumaraswamy College</strong> boasts of well-equipped classrooms, modern laboratories, a rich library, and digital learning resources that support the academic and co-curricular needs of our students. The college is affiliated with a reputed university and adheres to the standards set by the higher education authorities.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Our dedicated faculty members, administrative staff, and management work in harmony to maintain the institution’s tradition of excellence while embracing innovation and modernization. Beyond academics, the college encourages students to participate in cultural, sports, and social outreach programs, ensuring their all-round development.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Today, <strong>Sree Muthukumaraswamy College</strong> continues to build on its legacy, striving to empower every student with the skills, confidence, and values needed to succeed in an ever-changing world.
                    </p>

                    <h4 class="mt-5">Motto:</h4>
                    <p><em>“Knowledge, Discipline, and Service to Society.”</em></p>

                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <img src="~/img/history/history_1.png" alt="Sree Muthukumaraswamy College" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" style="max-width:600px;">
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
